article_title: Obamacare Q&A: Bouncing between Medi-Cal and Covered California
article_text: Another in a series of Q&A columns answering consumers’ questions about the Affordable Care Act. This week, Emily Bazar discusses what to do if you keep falling off Medi-Cal.
